Developer Terms of Use
des: Laundry and Dry Cleaning becomes easier with pickup and delivery services via Laundry on the Way. Just say 'Alexa, launch Laundry on the Way' to get started! Now you can tell Laundry on the Way you are ready for your clothes to be picked up! Just say, 'Alexa, tell Laundry on the Way to do my laundry' to let Laundry on the Way you want to schedule a pickup!
